Text.SourceString: I can't believe I woke up here this morning, right next to you. It's making me so happy.
Text.LocalizedString: I can't believe I woke up here this morning, right next to you. It's making me so happy.

Text.SourceString: I felt like a goddess yesterday in my wedding dress...dancing with you. Everything was just perfect.
Text.LocalizedString: I felt like a goddess yesterday in my wedding dress...dancing with you. Everything was just perfect.

Text.SourceString: I keep thinking about our vows. I absolutely loved yours – I almost cried right there on the podium, ha ha!
Text.LocalizedString: I keep thinking about our vows. I absolutely loved yours – I almost cried right there on the podium, ha ha!

Text.SourceString: I made this for you today, baby. It's a recipe from my underwater kingdom, with a touch of our farm's charm.
Text.LocalizedString: I made this for you today, baby. It's a recipe from my underwater kingdom, with a touch of our farm's charm.

Text.SourceString: I prepared your favorite meal today. Oh! Can't wait for you to try it, babe!
Text.LocalizedString: I prepared your favorite meal today. Oh! Can't wait for you to try it, babe!

Text.SourceString: I never realized how peaceful rain could be on land.
Text.LocalizedString: I never realized how peaceful rain could be on land.

Text.SourceString: The smell of rain is so different here than at sea. It's nice and comforting.
Text.LocalizedString: The smell of rain is so different here than at sea. It's nice and comforting.

Text.SourceString: I know it's silly, but lightning scares me.
Text.LocalizedString: I know it's silly, but lightning scares me.

Text.SourceString: Did you see that lightning? Oh my stars.//Oh, that lightning is really freaking me out! I gotta hide.
Text.LocalizedString: Did you see that lightning? Oh my stars.//Oh, that lightning is really freaking me out! I gotta hide.

Text.SourceString: Winter on land is so different from the sea's depths. It's a quiet, sure but it's super cold. Not a big fan.
Text.LocalizedString: Winter on land is so different from the sea's depths. It's a quiet, sure but it's super cold. Not a big fan.

Text.SourceString: Catching snowflakes is fun! How about we do that later, baby?//<portrait=happy>Let's make it interesting - if I catch more, I get to tell you what to do today.//But if you win...you get to be my boss for the day. Deal?
Text.LocalizedString: Catching snowflakes is fun! How about we do that later, baby?//<portrait=happy>Let's make it interesting - if I catch more, I get to tell you what to do today.//But if you win...you get to be my boss for the day. Deal?

Text.SourceString: I looked out of our window earlier and...um, I never imagined I'd see the day when the land gets covered in white, fluffy flakes.//It's enchanting.
Text.LocalizedString: I looked out of our window earlier and...um, I never imagined I'd see the day when the land gets covered in white, fluffy flakes.//It's enchanting.

Text.SourceString: I must admit, I'm not a fan of this cold Winter weather, baby. I miss the warmth of the Summer sun.
Text.LocalizedString: I must admit, I'm not a fan of this cold Winter weather, baby. I miss the warmth of the Summer sun.

Text.SourceString: Wow, the sun is really shining bright today! It feels amazing.
Text.LocalizedString: Wow, the sun is really shining bright today! It feels amazing.

Text.SourceString: We should definitely have a picnic, baby. With weather this perfect, it would be a shame not to enjoy it outdoors!
Text.LocalizedString: We should definitely have a picnic, baby. With weather this perfect, it would be a shame not to enjoy it outdoors!

Text.SourceString: I can't wait for Winter to end.
Text.LocalizedString: I can't wait for Winter to end.

Text.SourceString: It's freezing out there today, babe. How about we stay indoors, just you and me?//<portrait=happy>We could snuggle up inside a cozy blanket and keep each other warm.
Text.LocalizedString: It's freezing out there today, babe. How about we stay indoors, just you and me?//<portrait=happy>We could snuggle up inside a cozy blanket and keep each other warm.

Text.SourceString: I hate the cold, I really do...nobody hates it more than me. But you know, there's something peaceful about Winter nights, babe.//<portrait=happy>It's the way the stars seem to shine brighter against the dark sky. It almost makes the chill worth it.
Text.LocalizedString: I hate the cold, I really do...nobody hates it more than me. But you know, there's something peaceful about Winter nights, babe.//<portrait=happy>It's the way the stars seem to shine brighter against the dark sky. It almost makes the chill worth it.

Text.SourceString: Babe, there's ice forming on our window. Could you check it later? Maybe scrape it off for us, please?
Text.LocalizedString: Babe, there's ice forming on our window. Could you check it later? Maybe scrape it off for us, please?

Text.SourceString: I've put your gloves and hats in the top drawer, just in case you need more to stay warm.
Text.LocalizedString: I've put your gloves and hats in the top drawer, just in case you need more to stay warm.

Text.SourceString: I'm planning to change our sheets today to the thicker ones. I swear, I almost froze last night!
Text.LocalizedString: I'm planning to change our sheets today to the thicker ones. I swear, I almost froze last night!

Text.SourceString: Oops, I forgot to close the window in the extra room and the floor got all wet. But don't worry, I've already mopped it up.
Text.LocalizedString: Oops, I forgot to close the window in the extra room and the floor got all wet. But don't worry, I've already mopped it up.

Text.SourceString: Oh, babe, I've put your gloves and scarfs in the top drawer, just in case you need more layers.
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, babe, I've put your gloves and scarfs in the top drawer, just in case you need more layers.

Text.SourceString: How about we spend the day at the beach?//This weather is perfect for a swim.
Text.LocalizedString: How about we spend the day at the beach?//This weather is perfect for a swim.

Text.SourceString: Let's have a barbecue tonight. I can try cooking some land food! Should we invite your land friends?
Text.LocalizedString: Let's have a barbecue tonight. I can try cooking some land food! Should we invite your land friends?

Text.SourceString: Babe, just in case you forgot, I really love you. A lot. Ha ha!//That's never going to change.
Text.LocalizedString: Babe, just in case you forgot, I really love you. A lot. Ha ha!//That's never going to change.

Text.SourceString: I want you to remember something important, babe – I love you.
Text.LocalizedString: I want you to remember something important, babe – I love you.

Text.SourceString: Babe, I might not always say it, but I love you. So much.
Text.LocalizedString: Babe, I might not always say it, but I love you. So much.

Text.SourceString: You're looking really good today, babe. Got any special plans?
Text.LocalizedString: You're looking really good today, babe. Got any special plans?

Text.SourceString: Wow, that outfit looks incredible on you!
Text.LocalizedString: Wow, that outfit looks incredible on you!

Text.SourceString: I really like the way you've styled your hair today. It suits you so well. You look great, babe.
Text.LocalizedString: I really like the way you've styled your hair today. It suits you so well. You look great, babe.

Text.SourceString: How's your day been so far, babe? Anything exciting happen?
Text.LocalizedString: How's your day been so far, babe? Anything exciting happen?

Text.SourceString: Feeling a bit tired? I can make some snacks for us, if you'd like.
Text.LocalizedString: Feeling a bit tired? I can make some snacks for us, if you'd like.

Text.SourceString: What do you think about turning in early tonight? Some extra rest sounds nice.
Text.LocalizedString: What do you think about turning in early tonight? Some extra rest sounds nice.

Text.SourceString: I've been missing you a lot today, baby. Could really use one of your long hugs right about now.
Text.LocalizedString: I've been missing you a lot today, baby. Could really use one of your long hugs right about now.

Text.SourceString: How's everything looking out on our farm today, babe? All going well?
Text.LocalizedString: How's everything looking out on our farm today, babe? All going well?

Text.SourceString: I bumped into the mayor today. He asked me to send his regards to you.
Text.LocalizedString: I bumped into the mayor today. He asked me to send his regards to you.

Text.SourceString: It's been such a long day. I ended up cleaning the entire kitchen – wait till you see how it sparkles now.
Text.LocalizedString: It's been such a long day. I ended up cleaning the entire kitchen – wait till you see how it sparkles now.

Text.SourceString: I'm really tired, babe. Would you mind giving my legs a little massage? It would mean so much.
Text.LocalizedString: I'm really tired, babe. Would you mind giving my legs a little massage? It would mean so much.

Text.SourceString: I'm thinking a kelp salad tonight. Sounds yummy, right? Unless you've got a different craving, babe!
Text.LocalizedString: I'm thinking a kelp salad tonight. Sounds yummy, right? Unless you've got a different craving, babe!

Text.SourceString: I'm gonna try a new land recipe for dinner. Let's spice things up a bit!
Text.LocalizedString: I'm gonna try a new land recipe for dinner. Let's spice things up a bit!

Text.SourceString: That's it, I'm going to try making fried rice tonight! You like fried rice, right?//<portrait=annoyed>Okay, first things first – we need to get some rice ready. Do we have any?
Text.LocalizedString: That's it, I'm going to try making fried rice tonight! You like fried rice, right?//<portrait=annoyed>Okay, first things first – we need to get some rice ready. Do we have any?

Text.SourceString: Oh, guess what I found on the beach today? A super pretty shell! But I didn’t bring it home – left it there.
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, guess what I found on the beach today? A super pretty shell! But I didn’t bring it home – left it there.

Text.SourceString: Walking on these two legs is wild! I never knew how tricky stairs could be...and fun!
Text.LocalizedString: Walking on these two legs is wild! I never knew how tricky stairs could be...and fun!

Text.SourceString: I miss my tail sometimes, but having legs is an adventure!//<portrait=happy>Like, who knew hopping and skipping could be so much fun? Wanna see?
Text.LocalizedString: I miss my tail sometimes, but having legs is an adventure!//<portrait=happy>Like, who knew hopping and skipping could be so much fun? Wanna see?

Text.SourceString: These legs are something else, especially when I try running. Have you tried running, babe?
Text.LocalizedString: These legs are something else, especially when I try running. Have you tried running, babe?

Text.SourceString: Sometimes I wobble a bit, but hey, walking on legs is becoming my new favorite thing to do! And twirling...oh, I love twirling!
Text.LocalizedString: Sometimes I wobble a bit, but hey, walking on legs is becoming my new favorite thing to do! And twirling...oh, I love twirling!

Text.SourceString: You know, balancing on two legs is tricky, but I'm getting better at it every day. Don't you worry, babe!//Your wife here is a master of legs!
Text.LocalizedString: You know, balancing on two legs is tricky, but I'm getting better at it every day. Don't you worry, babe!//Your wife here is a master of legs!

Text.SourceString: I rolled my ankle the other day...these ankle things are so small. Of course, they roll so easily.
Text.LocalizedString: I rolled my ankle the other day...these ankle things are so small. Of course, they roll so easily.

Text.SourceString: Our land plants are growing so healthy, babe! They're so different from seaweed.//<portrait=concerned>I mean, they don't sway much, do they?
Text.LocalizedString: Our land plants are growing so healthy, babe! They're so different from seaweed.//<portrait=concerned>I mean, they don't sway much, do they?

Text.SourceString: I love this spot, babe, where I get to watch you farm.//<portrait=surprised>You're really good at walking. Good job!
Text.LocalizedString: I love this spot, babe, where I get to watch you farm.//<portrait=surprised>You're really good at walking. Good job!

Text.SourceString: Are you here to kiss me? Because if you aren't, you should be.
Text.LocalizedString: Are you here to kiss me? Because if you aren't, you should be.

Text.SourceString: Want me to get you some drinks, baby?
Text.LocalizedString: Want me to get you some drinks, baby?

Text.SourceString: Baby, our farm looks absolutely beautiful. You've poured so much love into it, and it really shows.//<portrait=happy>Thank you for working so hard on it.
Text.LocalizedString: Baby, our farm looks absolutely beautiful. You've poured so much love into it, and it really shows.//<portrait=happy>Thank you for working so hard on it.

Text.SourceString: Cooking land food is such a fun experiment. Like, who knew there were so many ways to prepare a potato?//You can fry them, bake them, even slice them up and turn them into sugar balls. It's amazing!
Text.LocalizedString: Cooking land food is such a fun experiment. Like, who knew there were so many ways to prepare a potato?//You can fry them, bake them, even slice them up and turn them into sugar balls. It's amazing!

Text.SourceString: I made a pie! But, um, it didn't turn out as great as I hoped, so I, uh...never mind that.
Text.LocalizedString: I made a pie! But, um, it didn't turn out as great as I hoped, so I, uh...never mind that.

Text.SourceString: We still have some Summer fruits left in the fridge.//How about we bake them into something delicious and send it to my parents?
Text.LocalizedString: We still have some Summer fruits left in the fridge.//How about we bake them into something delicious and send it to my parents?

Text.SourceString: Being here, I've grown to love the land as much as the sea. It's all part of one big, beautiful world.
Text.LocalizedString: Being here, I've grown to love the land as much as the sea. It's all part of one big, beautiful world.

Text.SourceString: I find myself talking to the plants and animals here, just like I did with the sea creatures. Nature is nature, no matter where you are.
Text.LocalizedString: I find myself talking to the plants and animals here, just like I did with the sea creatures. Nature is nature, no matter where you are.

Text.SourceString: Watching the sunrise over our farm is breathtaking. Never seen anything like it.
Text.LocalizedString: Watching the sunrise over our farm is breathtaking. Never seen anything like it.

Text.SourceString: Learning about your festivals is fascinating!
Text.LocalizedString: Learning about your festivals is fascinating!

Text.SourceString: Building a life here with you has been the best adventure, babe.
Text.LocalizedString: Building a life here with you has been the best adventure, babe.

Text.SourceString: I was just about to dive in for a swim, darling. Want to come along?
Text.LocalizedString: I was just about to dive in for a swim, darling. Want to come along?

Text.SourceString: The water's crystal clear today! Perfect timing to visit my parents, don't you think?
Text.LocalizedString: The water's crystal clear today! Perfect timing to visit my parents, don't you think?

Text.SourceString: You simply have to taste this seaweed salad Mom and I cooked earlier. It's delicious!
Text.LocalizedString: You simply have to taste this seaweed salad Mom and I cooked earlier. It's delicious!

Text.SourceString: Dad tried to understand our farm life. I explained about planting and harvesting, but he was so puzzled. Ha ha!
Text.LocalizedString: Dad tried to understand our farm life. I explained about planting and harvesting, but he was so puzzled. Ha ha!

Text.SourceString: Mom said hi, darling!
Text.LocalizedString: Mom said hi, darling!

Text.SourceString: It's refreshing to be back in the water. I love the buoyant feeling it gives.
Text.LocalizedString: It's refreshing to be back in the water. I love the buoyant feeling it gives.

Text.SourceString: I'm going to cook with Mom tonight. I think she really misses our cooking sessions.
Text.LocalizedString: I'm going to cook with Mom tonight. I think she really misses our cooking sessions.

Text.SourceString: Let me grab some ingredients from the store. I'm thinking of making kebabs tonight.
Text.LocalizedString: Let me grab some ingredients from the store. I'm thinking of making kebabs tonight.

Text.SourceString: Do you remember our first swim together? Feels like a lifetime ago, but so vivid in my mind.
Text.LocalizedString: Do you remember our first swim together? Feels like a lifetime ago, but so vivid in my mind.

Text.SourceString: Miss me yet?
Text.LocalizedString: Miss me yet?

Text.SourceString: You look amazing in the water, darling. It really suits you.
Text.LocalizedString: You look amazing in the water, darling. It really suits you.

Text.SourceString: Ah, it’s been a while since I’ve been here, hasn’t it? Feels like ages!
Text.LocalizedString: Ah, it’s been a while since I’ve been here, hasn’t it? Feels like ages!

Text.SourceString: I hope I still remember how to swim with a tail. Ha ha ha!
Text.LocalizedString: I hope I still remember how to swim with a tail. Ha ha ha!

Text.SourceString: I wonder if my favorite coral spot is still there. I should go check it out!
Text.LocalizedString: I wonder if my favorite coral spot is still there. I should go check it out!

Text.SourceString: I can’t wait to catch up with everyone here. I wonder if they’ve missed me!
Text.LocalizedString: I can’t wait to catch up with everyone here. I wonder if they’ve missed me!

Text.SourceString: Should we go to Sleepy Eel and grab something real quick? I'm craving their fancy drinks!
Text.LocalizedString: Should we go to Sleepy Eel and grab something real quick? I'm craving their fancy drinks!

Text.SourceString: Darling, Galoong’s new sculptures are incredible. We should definitely get something for our place.
Text.LocalizedString: Darling, Galoong’s new sculptures are incredible. We should definitely get something for our place.
